('b4b4778d-5844-4caf-9e6d-d14b820f6e44','v4-the-nibble-at-signing-1nijq1j','negotiation','The nibble at signing (negotiation)','Everything is agreed, the pens are out, and they ask for one more small concession as a formality. It is tiny — and it is also the third such formality. There is no clean option.'),
('871318fd-27fa-448e-923e-0c23ec2ec80f','v4-the-generous-first-offer-8xio1c','negotiation','The generous first offer (negotiation)','Their opening number is better than your target. Either you badly misread the market, or they know something you do not. Accepting fast feels like leaving money; probing risks unsettling it. Everyone is watching how you handle it.'),
('7d47f7fa-7da7-4646-832d-7f5ebd45351d','v4-the-anchor-you-set-urpnwt','negotiation','The anchor you set (negotiation)','Your own aggressive opening from last month is now being quoted back to you, after circumstances turned. The anchor you planted is working perfectly — against you. There is no clean option.'),
('c74c5802-e5aa-4962-9928-0e2ce9b3908e','v4-expiring-authority-ph8875','negotiation','Expiring authority (negotiation)','The person across the table loses signing authority at the end of the quarter, in 9 days. Their urgency is your leverage, or your trap. Everyone is watching how you handle it.'),
('75320e86-fea4-4155-bed9-cf6200b7c1b1','v4-the-generous-first-offer-1muako8','negotiation','The generous first offer II (negotiation)','Their opening number is better than your target. Either you badly misread the market, or they know something you do not. Accepting fast feels like leaving money; probing risks unsettling it. The clock is running.'),
