('ba61f77a-3324-440a-87cf-7f8c01926404','v4-the-nibble-at-signing-e89rtg','negotiation','The nibble at signing II (negotiation)','Everything is agreed, the pens are out, and they ask for one more small concession as a formality. It is tiny — and it is also the third such formality. The clock is running.'),
