('497d923f-a97b-4af9-9300-da260e0277e3','v4-the-nibble-at-signing-1g6o9jw','negotiation','The nibble at signing III (negotiation)','Everything is agreed, the pens are out, and they ask for one more small concession as a formality. It is tiny — and it is also the third such formality.'),
('5103545c-745d-4ac6-ab25-d7a4f35b55d3','v4-two-front-negotiation-5fz2vl','negotiation','Two-front negotiation (negotiation)','You are negotiating the same terms with your own side and the counterparty at once, and the concessions each demands are mutually exclusive. There is no clean option.'),
('0fdb37bb-eff7-453a-a12a-3601102dc7f4','v4-expiring-authority-wt6596','negotiation','Expiring authority II (negotiation)','The person across the table loses signing authority at the end of the quarter, in 6 days. Their urgency is your leverage, or your trap. Nobody senior is reachable.'),
('4e30910f-9eac-4272-aad0-44b93c98ede9','v4-expiring-authority-xuhzco','negotiation','Expiring authority III (negotiation)','The person across the table loses signing authority at the end of the quarter, in 5 days. Their urgency is your leverage, or your trap. There is no clean option.'),
