('fc026884-3860-4943-8953-6a66ae9ddff4','v4-the-nibble-at-signing-8rydy4','negotiation','The nibble at signing IV (negotiation)','Everything is agreed, the pens are out, and they ask for one more small concession as a formality. It is tiny — and it is also the third such formality. Everyone is watching how you handle it.'),
('5f3d6c18-56ea-4624-a21a-3cf41a8fb372','v4-the-recycled-confidence-1gd6dcg','social','The recycled confidence (social)','A private thing you told one person arrives back to you from a third. The chain has exactly two links, and both deny being the loose one. The clock is running.'),
('ff1113fa-1210-42f4-b9b5-7ca3e381aaa2','v4-the-plus-one-audit-1pl6s3d','social','The plus-one audit (social)','You discover you were the backup invite — the message meant for someone else made that plain. Attending anyway now has a script; declining writes a different one. The clock is running.'),
('29a19076-0794-4c01-a77a-cfee52583f11','v4-the-borrowed-money-silence-ehjnr0','social','The borrowed money silence (social)','A friend who borrowed money months ago has resumed posting vacations and has not mentioned the debt once. Raising it prices the friendship; not raising it compounds quietly. There is no clean option.'),
('ef6dad28-a159-4cdf-863a-ae18bcc4f8a4','v4-the-recycled-confidence-1y00p77','social','The recycled confidence II (social)','A private thing you told one person arrives back to you from a third. The chain has exactly two links, and both deny being the loose one. There is no clean option.'),
('3d80e2e8-aa9d-46b3-a5b2-2ea375fa98ef','v4-the-plus-one-audit-vqscn5','social','The plus-one audit II (social)','You discover you were the backup invite — the message meant for someone else made that plain. Attending anyway now has a script; declining writes a different one. Everyone is watching how you handle it.'),
('fcae74aa-9e93-4160-b0d8-5242bb911253','v4-the-recycled-confidence-pmyypg','social','The recycled confidence III (social)','A private thing you told one person arrives back to you from a third. The chain has exactly two links, and both deny being the loose one. Nobody senior is reachable.'),
('506ca546-c5d3-4b82-9045-aa0a35cf1dba','v4-the-one-sided-rivalry-kfz5q1','social','The one-sided rivalry (social)','Someone treats you as their measuring stick — cataloguing your wins, mirroring your moves. Naming it flatters you both badly; ignoring it feeds a story you are not in. Nobody senior is reachable.'),
('022a42c8-ee6c-4de4-9852-fd72b9074f84','v4-the-plus-one-audit-194u2wx','social','The plus-one audit III (social)','You discover you were the backup invite — the message meant for someone else made that plain. Attending anyway now has a script; declining writes a different one.'),
('4779003f-034e-45f8-a511-ef1e70100ceb','v4-the-borrowed-money-silence-12wo401','social','The borrowed money silence II (social)','A friend who borrowed money months ago has resumed posting vacations and has not mentioned the debt once. Raising it prices the friendship; not raising it compounds quietly. Everyone is watching how you handle it.'),
('552c4af8-c42e-4af8-8997-62e039c8c9d0','v4-the-correction-in-public-fn1ics','social','The correction in public (social)','You realize mid-meeting that the confident claim a friendly colleague just made is wrong, and the group is about to act on it. Correcting them costs them face; not correcting costs the group the outcome. The clock is running.'),
('f1f16bd9-0d06-4d8f-9f00-00e2df13f6fb','v4-the-correction-in-public-xlgygk','social','The correction in public II (social)','You realize mid-meeting that the confident claim a friendly colleague just made is wrong, and the group is about to act on it. Correcting them costs them face; not correcting costs the group the outcome.'),
