('33548b1d-0e51-4dce-816d-0ca76cbb87d1','v4-the-rollback-that-will-not-8lkd7v','crisis','The rollback that will not (crisis)','The obvious fix is rolling back the release — except the migration it shipped cannot be reversed, and the workaround only exists in one absent person''s head.'),
('3e507de8-45b7-4c2e-81ed-01bb056323fd','v4-donor-with-conditions-ao3v1z','crisis','Donor with conditions (crisis)','A rescue offer arrives mid-crisis with strings that solve this quarter and mortgage the next three years. The clock makes the strings look smaller than they are.'),
('30143580-9fe7-4d82-b1d3-4d0345834835','v4-the-overcorrection-window-iirccn','crisis','The overcorrection window (crisis)','Your first response to the incident was too aggressive and everyone now knows it. The correction you issue next will be read as the real policy. Nobody senior is reachable.'),
('dd7eaf71-ac5e-4857-93cb-e57cb83926a1','v4-the-rollback-that-will-not-118gova','crisis','The rollback that will not II (crisis)','The obvious fix is rolling back the release — except the migration it shipped cannot be reversed, and the workaround only exists in one absent person''s head. There is no clean option.'),
