('fdd543bb-38d1-4db2-95fe-609d7c0a8244','v4-insurance-ambiguity-1fc5nxe','crisis','Insurance ambiguity (crisis)','The policy that should cover this loss hinges on one clause with two readings. Filing the claim locks your account of events before you know which reading the insurer takes. Nobody senior is reachable.'),
